            <p><g type="cross">+</g> Ἀνεπά<unclear>ε</unclear> ὁ μακά<unclear>ρ</unclear><lb break="no"/>ιος Γεώργιος
               Βίκτω<lb break="no"/>ρ ἐν <expan><abbr>μη</abbr><ex>νὶ</ex></expan> Ξανθικῷ <num>ιςʹ</num> <expan><abbr>ἰ<lb break="no"/>νδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan> <num>ιβʹ</num> ἔτους υογʹ<g type="cross">+</g></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="elus0040.translation"
              corresp="#elus0040.transcription">
            <p>The Blessed George, son of Victor, went to his rest on the 16th of Xanthicos,
                    12th indiction, year 473.</p>
         </div>
